item.title: CVE-2023-6921|2024-08-02T08:42:08.657Z -- prestashow -- prestashop%20google%20integrator
item.description: Blind SQL Injection vulnerability in PrestaShow Google Integrator (PrestaShop addon) allows for data extraction and modification. This attack is possible via command insertion in one of the cookies.
